summary: An ordinance relating to the eminent domain proceedings under Ordinance No. 41403 affecting the alley between Blocks 33 and 34, Denny & Hoyt's Addition; providing for the setting aside of the judgements on the verdicts and the judgement confirming the assessment roll in Cause No. 146946, and the dismissal of said action; and, subject to such dismissal, repealing Ordinance No. 41403.
